{"tid":1928583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16/3/2020 抵制東方任務","createTime":"2020-03-16T13:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T22:26:01.000Z","uid":338095,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"3ccb79cb31f18970a4310a2af30b99c670ae6f78","tid":1928583,"uid":338095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SFVL8Pt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFVL8Pt.png&h=405974e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n❗️ 有見本專頁讚好人數增長速度理想，未來數天本專頁將會翻炒一D曾經被勤喻、但至今仍喺東方落廣告嘅商戶。請各位踴躍派嬲及留言，唔可以俾廣告商以為面對網民留言只要冷處理就可以不了了之❗️<br />\n【抵制東方日報每日任務】<br />\n😡1.派嬲 🗣2.洗版 🙅🏻&zwj;♀️♀3.永久抵制 👍🏻4.互like留言<br />\n<br />\n是日精選@16/3:<br />\n💩 維持健靈💩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vitagreenhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvitagreenhk%2F&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=8f59a9ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vitagreenhk/</a><br />\n👆去派嬲兼留言👆<br />\n<br />\n同何君堯、姚瑩瑩割蓆，抵讚。作為一間咁出名嘅公司，真係需要喺TVB同東方落廣告咩？<br />\n<br />\n留言Template:<br />\n東方日報多年來立場偏頗香港政府，自反修例示威起始，無視政府及警方暴力，抹黑示威者。以貴公司在香港之名氣及商譽，實在無在東方日報賣廣告之必要，但貴公司經上次勤喻後，仍不理我們的意見，令人失望。貴公司資源既取之於港人，亦應用之於港人，故希望你們考慮從東方日報撤回廣告，以免影響我們的購買意慾。<br />\n<br />\n#維持健靈 #Vitagreen"},{"pid":"4ccad4431c8e089cb0a7262872150a7c4b35b283","tid":1928583,"uid":154835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa3d29038ff8dc42938dc1102a49977d5c819cb","tid":1928583,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c444be1671131d0cd0cddbe4f29f648968acdac","tid":1928583,"uid":259246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pi