<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b07eff037e1eda65c2a08a1f165f66c01dc080","tid":1928583,"uid":143526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T19:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322fd1bfd4c75ac9c57252e071a0aa7c90aa6014","tid":1928583,"uid":37111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:29:47.000Z","msg":"幫手幫手"},{"pid":"6032fd66becc75d82cff2ff09e2fb65054c3bf4d","tid":1928583,"uid":344912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:39:25.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁 借位求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【超長文】所有自認和理非嘅手足 我地可以咁樣行多一步<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1928793/page/1?post=7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1928793/page/1?post=7</a>"},{"pid":"1b5692f05f557b284828e02c47a207f98630f79b","tid":1928583,"uid":329415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ccb79cb31f18970a4310a2af30b99c670ae6f78","tid":1928583,"uid":338095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SFVL8Pt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFVL8Pt.png&h=405974e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n❗️ 有見本專頁讚好人數增長速度理想，未來數天本專頁將會翻炒一D曾經被勤喻、但至今仍喺東方落廣告嘅商戶。請各位踴躍派嬲及留言，唔可以俾廣告商以為面對網民留言只要冷處理就可以不了了之❗️<br />\n【抵制東方日報每日任務】<br />\n😡1.派嬲 🗣2.洗版 🙅🏻&zwj;♀️♀3.永久抵制 👍🏻4.互like留言<br />\n<br />\n是日精選@16/3:<br />\n💩 維持健靈💩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vitagreenhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvitagreenhk%2F&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=8f59a9ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vitagreenhk/</a><br />\n👆去派嬲兼留言👆<br />\n<br />\n同何君堯、姚瑩瑩割蓆，抵讚。作為一間咁出名嘅公司，真係需要喺TVB同東方落廣告咩？<br />\n<br />\n留言Template:<br />\n東方日報多年來立場偏頗香港政府，自反修例示威起始，無視政府及警方暴力，抹黑示威者。以貴公司在香港之名氣及商譽，實在無在東方日報賣廣告之必要，但貴公司經上次勤喻後，仍不理我們的意見，令人失望。貴公司資源既取之於港人，亦應用之於港人，故希望你們考慮從東方日報撤回廣告，以免影響我們的購買意慾。<br />\n<br />\n#維持健靈 #Vitagreen"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2ef421beff6903677d3ca2e2e4b05be8f130e4","tid":1928583,"uid":281713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T02:44:08.000Z","msg":"P牌推！"},{"pid":"872600603067f2dfbc9008dda1d7ef344f8d3919","tid":1928583,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef82daa1c38708b5780cb08955b4a1ca723e1afc","tid":1928583,"uid":305428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"已做"}],"pinned":{"pid":"5e56e754de4cb859b19dfdc2aad41d2716cf998e","tid":1928583,"uid":305428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T05:10:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/nooncc689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnooncc689&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=18e3c7e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nooncc689</a><br />\n<br />\n請樓主pin一pin，呢個係抵制東方嘅tg channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可以用埋tg一齊隊冧白粉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}